; kree script. entered in 3/31/96

VARIABLE SETPLAYERTECH
VARIABLE ADDTECH
VARIABLE FINDTECHS
VARIABLE TECHCHECK
VARIABLE KREEHAHA
VARIABLE RANDOMTECH
VARIABLE TECHZERO
VARIABLE CHECKPLRTECH
VARIABLE KREEROOMX

MACRO 58

IFVAR TIM = 0
  IFVAR INTNUM70 ! 0
    EQUAL INTNUM70 0
  ENDIF
ENDIF

IFVAR RNUM = 780
  IFVAR DEAD = 1
    ADD INTNUM70 1
    GMMSG %n is being saved!
    AFFECT 780
    ECHO ALL A swirling light begins to form a powerful eddy in the air.
    ECHO ALL Suddenly, a loud snap shakes the room and blinding flash fills the room.
    ECHO PLAYER You feel yourself being pullled...
    ECHO OTHERS As suddenly as the maelstorm of power rose, it subsides into nothingness.
    MOVE 3713
    AFFECT 3713
    ECHO OTHERS A swirling eddy of light and steam forms in air.
    ECHO OTHERS Suddenly, a loud snap can be heard and %n's body appears on the platform.
    ECHO PLAYER A different room swirls into focus, and you find yourself lying on a platform with a pentagram.
    AFFECT 780
    ECHO OTHERS You notice %n is gone.
  ENDIF
ENDIF

